{
  "texts": [
    "Forman et al.",
    "conducted a similar online survey exploring high school students' perceptions towards ChatGPT [46].",
    "The analysis of 71 responses revealed students' positive attitude towards GenAI technology, as they are assuming it to play a role long term.",
    "Moreover, students reported to rely on GenAI tools to help save time during assignments and projects.",
    "Raman et al. [2] investigated university students' adoption of ChatGPT by addressing the attributes relative advantage, compatibility, ease of use, observability, and trialability."
  ]
}